### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/health
Accept: application/json

###
### Create topic
POST http://localhost:8080/api/topics
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{"name":"orders"}

###
### List topics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/topics
Accept: application/json

###
### Topic details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/topics/orders
Accept: application/json

###
### Delete topic
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/topics/orders
Accept: application/json

###
### Create queue (FIFO)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/queues
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{"name":"tasks","mode":"FIFO"}

###
### Create queue (PRIORITY)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/queues
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{"name":"tasks_priority","mode":"PRIORITY"}

###
### List queues
GET http://localhost:8080/api/queues
Accept: application/json

###
### Queue details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/queues/tasks
Accept: application/json

###
### Delete queue
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/queues/tasks
Accept: application/json
